OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774271469
OL,3,CInquest opens into deaths of father
OL,4,Cand daughter in air fryer fire
OL,6,FAn inquest has opened into the deaths
OL,7,Fof a father and his daughter in a fire
OL,8,Fcaused by an air fryer at their
OL,9,FChinese restaurant.
OL,11,FYu Li, 45, and 11-year-old Sophie
OL,12,FWanshi Li suffered fatal injuries in
OL,13,Fthe incident at the Golden Phoenix on
OL,14,FManby Middlegate, Grimoldby, near
OL,15,FLouth, Lincolnshire, on 18 February.
OL,17,FInvestigators from Lincolnshire Fire
OL,18,Fand Rescue Service said the blaze was
OL,19,Fstarted accidentally by an air fryer.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
