FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774271469
OL,3,CInquest opens into deaths of father
OL,4,Cand daughter in air fryer fire
OL,6,FAn inquest at Grimsby Town Hall heard
OL,7,FSophie's preliminary cause of death
OL,8,Fwas smoke inhalation.
OL,10,FMr Li's cause of death is yet to be
OL,11,Fdetermined.
OL,13,FA woman in her 30s, who was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital in a serious condition
OL,15,Ffollowing the blaze, remains in
OL,16,Fhospital in Nottingham in a stable
OL,17,Fcondition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774271469
OL,3,CInquest opens into deaths of father
OL,4,Cand daughter in air fryer fire
OL,6,FTwo men in their 40s and two children
OL,7,Funder 10, were also taken to hospital
OL,8,Fand were later discharged. Passers-by
OL,9,Fhelped to rescue two younger children.
OL,11,FThe inquest was adjourned for further
OL,12,Finvestigations
OL,14,FA Go Fund Me page set up to support
OL,15,Fthe Li family has raised more than
OL,16,F#12,000.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
