PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774271469
OL,3,CInquest opens into deaths of father
OL,4,Cand daughter in air fryer fire
OL,6,FFamily friend William Wong, said: "As
OL,7,Fa long time friend of the family, the
OL,8,Ffamily and I have found some comfort
OL,9,Ffrom the kind and supportive
OL,10,Fcommunity, and the public in Grimoldby
OL,11,Fand North Thoresby. On behalf of Li's
OL,12,Ffamily, I would like to say thank you
OL,13,Ffor your kindness.
OL,15,F"A special thanks to the passers-by,
OL,16,Fwho bravely went into the fire
OL,17,Fengulfed property to help and rescue
OL,18,Fthe two younger children. From the
OL,19,Fbottom of my heart and on behalf of
OL,20,Fthe family, I can't thank you enough."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
